      <div class="gardens__body">
          <p>Many longtime Comox Valley residents are always surprised to discover a 
              local hidden gem known as the Anderton Therapeutic Gardens (ATGS). The Gardens opened in 1998 
              after two years of planning by founders Bill and Joy Georgeson. </p>

              <p>Their dream was to create a garden that would enhance a visitor’s overall well-being in a 
                  tranquil, idyllic setting. This two-acre parcel of land is located directly behind the Nursery
                   on Anderton Road and stands as a proud testament to the thousands of hours of volunteer work 
                   that have gone into maintaining the gardens over the years.</p>
                   <p class="extra-m">We invite you to enjoy this jewel in our neighborhood.</p>
